# grok-cli — Overview

## Router (src/router)
- message_bus.rs — typed inter-agent message passing
- employer.rs — dry-run simulation before destructive ops
- employer.rs — repository structure exploration queries
- cpu_router.rs — core tool loop call API — execute tools → append result → repeat
- app_router.rs — application-level routing (chain vs code vs plan)
- backend.rs — backend async trait (send + stream + health)
- backends/grok.rs — AI Grok backend, think-reason handling
- request.rs / response.rs — RouterRequest / RouterResponse
- router_errors.rs — MaxRouterItems, ApiError, Timeout variants

## Context & Prompt (src/context)
- engine.rs — orchestrates all context subsystems per turn
- prompt_builder.rs — assembles system prompt from DNA, knowledge, skills
- prompt_applicator.rs — applies transformers (goal injection, Bayesian hints)
- prompt_cache.rs / prompt_delta.rs — incremental prompt caching
- prompt_diff.rs — diffs consecutive prompts for delta sends
- session_manager.rs — session context lifecycle cleanup
- session_summarizer.rs — LLM-driven compression of old turns into summary
- token_counter.rs / token_cache.rs — fast char-token estimation + cache
- context_targets.rs — per-model token budgets
- belief_states.rs — tracks context-level belief state
- tool_optimizer.rs — prunes tool list to minimum needed per turn

## Bayesian Engine (src/bayes)
- engine.rs — BayesianEngine: posterior inference
- belief_graph.rs — DAG of beliefs with conditional dependencies
- priors.rs — compiled probability priors per intent category
- likelihoods.rs — evidence likelihood tables
- bayes_update.rs — Bayes update logic
- profiles.rs — per-session user + task profile

## RAG / Knowledge (src/rag)
- api.rs — public retrieval API
- compression.rs — chunk compression
- persistence.rs — index serialization/deserialization
- api_integrations.rs — ACP session hooks
- integration.rs — DNA-shaped retrieval weighting
- graph/ — code graph builder, node, edge, project_graph
- index/ — chunk indexing, vector store, lookup
- parser/ — lexer, symbol extraction
- retrieval/ — cosine similarity, BM25, hybrid search

